PrecisAmendments to the PATENT RULES guaranteeing all Canadians a means for depositing documents with the Canadian Patent Office, facilitating and improving the filing of patent documents across Canada by establishing a method to determine a specific delivery date, and providing the Commissioner with flexibility to designate establishments for the delivery of correspondence.

precis:
Amendments to the PATENT RULES guaranteeing all Canadians a means for
depositing documents with the Canadian Patent Office, facilitating and
improving the filing of patent documents across Canada by establishing a
method to determine a specific delivery date, and providing the
Commissioner with flexibility to designate establishments for the delivery
of correspondence.
